{"tid":716623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你叫 l____ch__係carousell走過數又比人拉左可以入一入黎","createTime":"2018-06-25T11:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T07:17:33.000Z","uid":78085,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"46208c46f30b76c6039396edb4e97169ed4976ea","tid":716623,"uid":78085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟之前係carousell比人走數 <br />\n講緊好少錢 同埋我唔等錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能9成連登仔會話多一事不如少一事 <br />\n不過除左我應該都有其他師兄被走數 <br />\n所以報左案 警方有一路跟進 最近話已經拉左 <br />\n遲少少等我confirm上庭charge定私了<br />\n<br />\n如果你見到係自己可以搵方法聯絡我 <br />\n有興趣聽下你解釋 <br />\nAcct名就保密 佢自己應該估到係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080a2a757d019be1fd19e77e6ecd2a6ce46ff9f6","tid":716623,"uid":85716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"點聯絡你 有冇tg"},{"pid":"5a50083c622e02a5af3ad9252a308a6d4f7a9369","tid":716623,"uid":75026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9cd5a439ca16424eed029691810a144823e9541","tid":716623,"uid":186800,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"一定要落charge<br />\n你想像下佢見你入完數笑笑口kill app個樣"},{"pid":"3bd428bbf66127399d3f8a3665b72c9d3af363c1","tid":716623,"uid":75026,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5803d6e126ccd3051bc0496a3a066591e0f45309","tid":716623,"uid":186800,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3bd428bbf66127399d3f8a3665b72c9d3af363c1","tid":716623,"uid":75026,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"a9cd5a439ca16424eed029691810a144823e9541","tid":716623,"uid":186800,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"一定要落charge<br />\n你想像下佢見你入完數笑笑口kill app個樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆